       Name: Valor Crit
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_IGNORE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 0
 Wait Beats: 0
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: Your righteous fury fades.
Acquisition:
   None (internal affect holder)
Description:
   Valor Crit is an internal affect holder associated with the Cloak:Valor
   ability used by Paladins. It tracks and applies the guaranteed critical
   strike proc that Cloak:Valor periodically grants. When this affect is
   active, the Paladin's next attack is guaranteed to critically strike.

   This is not a castable ability. The affect is applied automatically by
   the Cloak:Valor system when its proc condition is met. Staff may see
   this affect on players who have Cloak:Valor active and have accumulated
   sufficient righteous fury charges. The wear-off message "Your righteous
   fury fades" indicates that the guaranteed critical window has passed
   without being consumed.
*******************************************************************************
